00:36:12,917 --> 00:36:14,167
<font color="#00ffff">Dia telah dibunuh.</font>

341
00:36:15,750 --> 00:36:16,833
<font color="#00ffff">Apa?</font>

342
00:36:18,125 --> 00:36:19,708
<font color="#00ffff">Oleh Winter Soldier.</font>

343
00:36:23,542 --> 00:36:24,822
<font color="#00ffff">Dan dia adalah aku.</font>

344
00:36:27,958 --> 00:36:29,000
<font color="#00ffff">Kenapa?</font>

345
00:36:32,792 --> 00:36:34,167
<font color="#00ffff">Aku tiada pilihan.</font>

346
00:38:09,208 --> 00:38:10,458
<font color="#00ffff">Apa yang kau mahu, Black Falcon?</font>

347
00:38:10,542 --> 00:38:12,375
<font color="#00ffff">Hei, kau kena belajar adab.</font>

348
00:38:13,625 --> 00:38:15,333
<font color="#00ffff">Dia bukan lagi Falcon,</font>

349
00:38:16,792 --> 00:38:17,917
<font color="#00ffff">tapi dia masih Hitam.</font>

350
00:38:24,958 --> 00:38:26,500
<font color="#00ffff">Aku lihat tindakan kau
