358
00:38:57,375 --> 00:38:58,458
<font color="#00ffff">Aku bersependapat.</font>

359
00:38:59,125 --> 00:39:00,708
<font color="#00ffff">Tapi aku tahu apa
yang perlu aku lakukan.</font>

360
00:39:02,750 --> 00:39:05,750
<font color="#00ffff">Jadi Captain America kulit hitam, ya?</font>

361
00:39:07,042 --> 00:39:08,167
<font color="#00ffff">Benar.</font>

362
00:39:11,792 --> 00:39:15,000
<font color="#00ffff">Perjuangan kau takkan mudah, Sam.</font>

363
00:39:16,542 --> 00:39:17,583
<font color="#00ffff">Ya, mungkin aku akan gagal.</font>

364
00:39:19,125 --> 00:39:20,458
<font color="#00ffff">Mungkin aku akan mati.</font>

365
00:39:21,375 --> 00:39:22,458
<font color="#00ffff">Tapi...</font>

366
00:39:23,125 --> 00:39:24,250
<font color="#00ffff">Kita yang membina negara ini.</font>

367
00:39:25,083 --> 00:39:26,167
<font color="#00ffff">Berkorban demi negara ini.</font>

368
00:39:27,708 --> 00:39:30,375
<font color="#00ffff">Tiada sesiapa yang boleh menghalang aku
untuk berjuang untuk negara ini.</font>

369
00:39:31,625 --> 00:39:34,208
